4.content:
Hello Karl!

Welcome to Trapezoid Health!
I am Daniel, the managing director of the company.
4.name: Dialogue State

17.content: Congratulations on your new job as a Supply Chain Director.
17.name: Dialogue State

293.content: Now let me show you your office.
293.name: Dialogue State

23137.content: Your task is to ensure sufficient {drugName} inventory to meet future unexpected demand.
23137.name: Dialogue State

23139.content: Just keep in mind that there are high costs for maintaining too much inventory.
23139.name: Dialogue State

24121.content: You can review your goal by clicking on this button.
24121.name: Dialogue State

24153.action_text: Goal: Minimize Cost! (Total cost: ${costTotal}) Ensure sufficient {drugName} inventory to meat future unexpected demands.

24294.content: You can check the inventory costs by clicking on this button.
24294.name: Dialogue State

24315.action_text: Patients treated with replacement drugs: Urgent patients {cumUntreatedU} (${cumRepCostU}) Non-urgent patients {cumUntreatedNU} (${cumRepCostNU}) Total patients {cumLost} (${cumRepCostTotal})

26264.content: Your main goal is to minimize the overall cost to the company.
26264.name: Dialogue State

26265.content: The overall cost consists of the inventory cost and the cost of backlog in case we're out of {drugName}.
26265.name: Dialogue State

28119.content: Click or tap anywhere on the screen to move the game forward.
28119.name: Dialogue State

28120.content: This game is part of a study on pharmaceutical supply chains.
28120.name: Dialogue State

28122.content: You will be deciding how much Saline to order from your supplier.
28122.name: Dialogue State

28149.content: In case you're not familiar with Saline solution, here is what it looks like. It is a mixture of sodium chloride in water which has a number of uses in medicine.
28149.name: Dialogue State
